00:33:27,364 --> 00:33:29,424
You're right.

513
00:33:30,554 --> 00:33:34,464
Hey, look at this color. Look.

514
00:33:35,374 --> 00:33:38,744
It's tasty. It's so tasty.

515
00:33:40,244 --> 00:33:41,904
Here.

516
00:33:44,854 --> 00:33:47,184
Wow.

517
00:33:47,184 --> 00:33:50,144
