 - My gosh.

523
00:34:09,084 --> 00:34:13,104
Here you go, Queen Dowager.

524
00:34:13,104 --> 00:34:15,944
What do you think?

525
00:34:20,574 --> 00:34:23,364
Is it because my son bought this with the money he earned?

526
00:34:23,364 --> 00:34:25,804
It really tastes amazing.

527
00:34:25,804 --> 00:34:30,084
Hey, Myeong Dong. You should eat more, too.

528
00:34:30,084 --> 00:34:31,994
Say, ah. Say, ah.

529
00:34:31,994 --> 00:34:34,654
I'm eating.

530
00:34:34,654 --> 00:34:40,154
