00:34:40,154 --> 00:34:41,574
Huh?

532
00:34:41,574 --> 00:34:44,824
Yes. I'm telling you.

533
00:34:44,824 --> 00:34:47,474
How many times do you have to ask?

534
00:34:47,474 --> 00:34:50,644
It's because I'm happy. I'm happy.

535
00:34:50,644 --> 00:34:55,454
Do you remember the last time you made money?

536
00:34:55,454 --> 00:34:59,554
