539
00:35:05,684 --> 00:35:09,254
I don't care if it gets smelly.

540
00:35:09,254 --> 00:35:15,544
I'll keep it on even when I'm sleeping since my son bought it for me.

541
00:35:15,544 --> 00:35:17,954
Me, too. Me, too.

542
00:35:19,644 --> 00:35:20,784
I'm home.

543
00:35:20,784 --> 00:35:24,644
- Hey, my son. Welcome home. Welcome. 
 - Welcome home.

544
00:35:24,644 --> 00:35:26,684
Pil Sung, get changed and join us.

545
00:35:26,684 --> 00:35:29,604
Dad bought beef for us today.

546
00:35:30,394 --> 00:35:31,804
Okay.

547
00:35:31,804 --> 00:35:33,774
Yes, join us soon.

548
00:35:34,964 --> 00:35:36,844
Wow...

549
00:35:48,674 --> 00:35:51,314
I'll get changed and join you in a bit.

550
00:35:52,214 --> 00:35:54,664
Did Park Do Ra lash out on you again?

