552
00:35:57,374 --> 00:35:58,854
This is no good.

553
00:35:58,854 --> 00:36:02,144
I need to meet up with that Park Do Ra soon.

554
00:36:02,144 --> 00:36:06,874
Auntie, why would you meet up with her?

