558
00:36:16,814 --> 00:36:21,604
I'm so pissed thinking about what I saw. I haven't had beef in a while,

559
00:36:21,604 --> 00:36:26,254
but I couldn't even taste what I was eating, okay?

560
00:36:27,004 --> 00:36:30,674
Thinking about what she did to you makes my blood flow backward.

561
00:36:30,674 --> 00:36:34,214
