00:36:47,224 --> 00:36:49,704
What are you talking about right now?

567
00:36:51,544 --> 00:36:53,474
- M-Mom. 
 - Unni.

568
00:36:53,474 --> 00:36:57,734
Well, what are you talking about?

569
00:36:57,734 --> 00:37:03,974
Pil Sung, do you work with Park Do Ra right now?

570
00:37:03,974 --> 00:37:08,494
Auntie, you said Park Do Ra scolded him like hell?

571
00:37:08,494 --> 00:37:11,244
Gosh, what are you talking about, Auntie?

572
00:37:11,244 --> 00:37:14,134
What are you all talking about?

573
00:37:14,134 --> 00:37:18,024
Go Pil Sung, won't you tell me the truth?

