580
00:37:43,534 --> 00:37:45,144
I was exaggerating a bit.

581
00:37:45,144 --> 00:37:46,864
He didn't act like a servant, Unni.

582
00:37:46,864 --> 00:37:50,604
Pil Sung, are you out of your mind?

583
00:37:50,604 --> 00:37:54,444
How could you work with her and be humiliated by her?

584
00:37:54,444 --> 00:37:58,454
You should've said you couldn't work with her and asked to be transferred to another team.

585
00:37:58,454 --> 00:38:03,604
At first, I didn't want to when I heard she was the lead, but...

586
00:38:03,604 --> 00:38:06,124
there was nothing I could've done.

587
00:38:06,124 --> 00:38:09,184
Yes, it's not easy to work for a company.

588
00:38:09,184 --> 00:38:11,254
You're expected to do what you're told to.

589
00:38:11,254 --> 00:38:14,814
