590
00:38:14,814 --> 00:38:17,544
He can't ask them to switch teams for him.

591
00:38:17,544 --> 00:38:19,874
Yes, yes. Of course not.

592
00:38:19,874 --> 00:38:26,644
At least she didn't recognize Pil Sung. That's a relief.

593
00:38:26,644 --> 00:38:29,964
Hey. Don't you agree, Hyeon Cheol?

594
00:38:29,964 --> 00:38:33,134
Pardon? Oh, yes.

595
00:38:33,134 --> 00:38:35,984
Gosh, I'm so upset.

596
00:38:35,984 --> 00:38:38,844
Park Do Ra, that bitch. How dare she?

597
00:38:38,844 --> 00:38:43,124
What makes her think she could bully my son?

598
00:38:44,714 --> 00:38:49,574
Mom, Do Ra doesn't know who I am. She knows nothing.

599
00:38:49,574 --> 00:38:53,834
She's a superstar, and I'm the youngest assistant director on set.

600
00:38:53,834 --> 00:38:56,264
But I made a mistake while working. So...

601
00:38:56,264 --> 00:39:00,954
I should be responsible for the mistake I made.

602
00:39:00,954 --> 00:39:05,044
Mom, Dad, Grandma, and Auntie.

603
00:39:05,044 --> 00:39:07,114
Don't worry so much.

604
00:39:07,804 --> 00:39:11,304
I'll take good care of it. I'm really okay.

605
00:39:18,584 --> 00:39:21,384
Gosh, what's going on, anyway?

606
00:39:21,384 --> 00:39:22,974
Gosh, my head hurts.

607
00:39:22,974 --> 00:39:25,594
Gosh, what a headache. Aigoo...

608
00:39:25,594 --> 00:39:29,454
Yes, Unni. What he said makes sense.

609
00:39:29,454 --> 00:39:32,474
It's not like he has control over the situation.

610
00:39:32,474 --> 00:39:36,864
And they're already halfway through shooting. It'll end soon.

611
00:39:36,864 --> 00:39:39,554
They'd never see each other again once this drama ends.

612
00:39:39,554 --> 00:39:44,774
Yes, Pil Sung will take care of everything.

613
00:39:57,914 --> 00:40:04,254
By the way, I felt kind of bad for Assistant Director Go.

614
00:40:04,254 --> 00:40:06,514
Looks like he just did what he was told to.

615
00:40:06,514 --> 00:40:11,044
He was humoring Cha Bong Soo, so the shooting goes smoothly.

616
00:40:11,044 --> 00:40:14,804
I don't think he said that because he hates you.

617
00:40:14,804 --> 00:40:17,514
Don't mention Go Pil Sung with me from now on.

618
00:40:17,514 --> 00:40:19,434
I don't want to hear it.

619
00:40:20,534 --> 00:40:24,784
And you'd better not talk to him, either. Understand?

620
00:40:25,534 --> 00:40:27,434
Okay, Noona.

621
00:40:33,754 --> 00:40:36,064
We're here, Noona.

622
00:40:42,104 --> 00:40:43,304
You can leave.

623
00:40:43,304 --> 00:40:45,964
Pardon? I thought you were drinking.

624
00:40:45,964 --> 00:40:47,104
I'll wait here.

625
00:40:47,104 --> 00:40:49,004
No, it's okay. You should go.

626
00:40:49,004 --> 00:40:51,844
You said it's your mother's birthday today.

627
00:40:51,844 --> 00:40:54,774
Take her the gift in the back.

628
00:40:55,344 --> 00:40:56,994
Bye.

629
00:41:13,574 --> 00:41:16,894
Yes, President. This is Jae Dong.

630
00:41:26,654 --> 00:41:29,234
 But it's so hard for me to humor her, too. 

631
00:41:29,234 --> 00:41:31,454
 I could see why people call her "Bbakdora." 

632
00:41:31,454 --> 00:41:33,644
 She drives me nuts 12 times a day! 

633
00:41:33,644 --> 00:41:37,664
 So we could finish the drama successfully... 

634
00:41:37,664 --> 00:41:40,994
But still, he couldn't have played me like that.

635
00:41:42,304 --> 00:41:44,994
Bat. Scoundrel.

636
00:41:44,994 --> 00:41:47,924
There's no one trustworthy in this world.

637
00:41:54,464 --> 00:41:56,674
Are you Ms. Park Do Ra, by chance?

638
00:42:01,414 --> 00:42:03,664
Yes.

639
00:42:03,664 --> 00:42:05,594
It really was you, Ms. Park.

640
00:42:05,594 --> 00:42:08,024
I can't believe I ran into you here.

641
00:42:08,024 --> 00:42:11,094
- What a coincidence. 
 - President Gong.

642
00:42:11,094 --> 00:42:12,894
What brings you here?

643
00:42:12,894 --> 00:42:16,694
I come here sometimes whenever I want to drink alone after work.

644
00:42:17,544 --> 00:42:19,514
Me, too. Me, too.

645
00:42:19,514 --> 00:42:24,914
I come whenever I want to drink because it's quiet and private here.

646
00:42:25,914 --> 00:42:28,084
Anyway, this is crazy.

647
00:42:28,084 --> 00:42:30,234
I can't believe I ran into you here.

648
00:42:30,234 --> 00:42:32,684
Are you alone, Do Ra? I am, too.

649
00:42:32,684 --> 00:42:34,974
Should we drink together? It's not easy to run into each other like this.

650
00:42:34,974 --> 00:42:39,464
Sounds good. Since you've been doing so much for me,

651
00:42:39,464 --> 00:42:42,124
I really wanted to treat you to a drink.

652
00:42:42,124 --> 00:42:44,264
It's my treat tonight.

653
00:42:44,774 --> 00:42:46,484
Really?

654
00:42:46,484 --> 00:42:49,304
Wow, I'd be honored.

655
00:42:52,554 --> 00:42:55,814
- Cheers. 
 - Cheers.

656
00:43:05,094 --> 00:43:06,394
Drink slowly.

657
00:43:06,394 --> 00:43:09,284
You look a bit drunk already.

658
00:43:09,284 --> 00:43:10,824
It's okay.

659
00:43:10,824 --> 00:43:14,084
You drink, so you get drunk.

660
00:43:15,134 --> 00:43:18,004
Sometimes, you feel like getting drunk.

661
00:43:18,004 --> 00:43:21,634
You want to get drunk and forget everything.

662
00:43:21,634 --> 00:43:24,334
Don't you ever feel that way?

663
00:43:24,334 --> 00:43:26,294
Of course, I do.

664
00:43:26,294 --> 00:43:29,654
All sorts of things happen in life.

665
00:43:29,654 --> 00:43:34,514
I checked the shooting schedule. It looked pretty intense since it's almost over now.

666
00:43:34,514 --> 00:43:36,294
You must be very tired.

667
00:43:39,364 --> 00:43:41,594
Work isn't hard.

668
00:43:41,594 --> 00:43:43,954
But people are.

669
00:43:43,954 --> 00:43:45,414
People?

670
00:43:46,154 --> 00:43:47,924
People, you said?

671
00:43:48,624 --> 00:43:50,814
Is someone giving you a hard time?

672
00:43:50,814 --> 00:43:54,424
Who is it? Let me scold them for you.

673
00:43:55,504 --> 00:43:57,324
- Really? 
 - Of course.

674
00:43:57,324 --> 00:44:00,094
I'll always be your fan, no matter what.

675
00:44:00,094 --> 00:44:03,794
Let me know if anyone's giving you a hard time. I'll...

676
00:44:03,794 --> 00:44:06,894
- take care of everything for you. 
 - Wow...

677
00:44:07,714 --> 00:44:11,224
Wow, you're so cool, President Gong.

678
00:44:11,224 --> 00:44:14,464
Thank you for saying that.

679
00:44:14,464 --> 00:44:16,274
You're the best, President Gong.

680
00:44:17,014 --> 00:44:18,574
The best.

681
00:44:28,834 --> 00:44:31,704
 What kind of scoundrel are you? 

682
00:44:34,844 --> 00:44:36,454
Yes.

683
00:44:37,834 --> 00:44:41,004
I should beg her until she feels better.

684
00:44:41,004 --> 00:44:43,104
