00:45:18,304 --> 00:45:20,234
When did we get here?

689
00:45:20,234 --> 00:45:22,094
Just now.

690
00:45:22,094 --> 00:45:24,204
Let's go. I'll walk you to the door.

691
00:45:24,204 --> 00:45:26,204
No, no, no. I can go on my own.

692
00:45:26,204 --> 00:45:28,774
No, no, no. I can go on my own.

693
00:45:28,774 --> 00:45:31,224
Thank you.

694
00:45:32,594 --> 00:45:35,204
See? You almost fell.

695
00:45:35,204 --> 00:45:39,054
I'll walk you just to the elevator, then.

696
00:45:39,054 --> 00:45:44,644
Gosh, President Gong, you're so kind.

697
00:45:44,644 --> 00:45:47,776
Thank you.

698
00:45:48,684 --> 00:45:50,244
Don't mention it.

699
00:45:50,244 --> 00:45:52,014
It's nothing. Let's go.

700
00:45:52,014 --> 00:45:56,864
Okay. I think I'm a bit drunk.

701
00:45:56,864 --> 00:45:58,984
Let's go.

702
00:46:02,784 --> 00:46:05,574
President Gong looks fine.

703
00:46:05,574 --> 00:46:09,054
Why did she drink so much and get drunk?

704
00:46:09,954 --> 00:46:12,834
Geez, I won't be able to talk to her tonight.

705
00:46:15,704 --> 00:46:17,864
Yes, Yoon Hee.

706
00:46:19,984 --> 00:46:21,654
What did you say?

707
00:46:22,884 --> 00:46:25,084
The same hotel?

708
00:46:25,784 --> 00:46:29,394
Okay, I'll be right there. Wait for me.

709
00:46:36,864 --> 00:46:39,264
Looks like he has a girlfriend.

710
00:46:42,914 --> 00:46:46,004
By the way, why did he drink so late

711
00:46:46,004 --> 00:46:50,164
with Park Do Ra when he has a girlfriend?

712
00:46:55,554 --> 00:46:57,254
What's this?

713
00:46:57,254 --> 00:47:01,894
Will you leave me after taking it or without taking it?

714
00:47:09,504 --> 00:47:10,924
Thank you, Oppa.

715
00:47:10,924 --> 00:47:14,014
Yes, I want to thank you for everything, too.

716
00:47:14,014 --> 00:47:16,674
I wish you all the best.

717
00:47:17,374 --> 00:47:19,574
Don't contact me ever again.

718
00:47:30,204 --> 00:47:31,794
Honey, I'm home.

719
00:47:31,794 --> 00:47:34,624
You're home.

720
00:47:34,624 --> 00:47:35,964
What's that?

721
00:47:35,964 --> 00:47:37,684
This?

722
00:47:37,684 --> 00:47:43,304
I got it because I was worried after seeing your test result.

723
00:47:43,304 --> 00:47:45,674
