724
00:47:45,674 --> 00:47:52,904
Here. Make sure to take it regularly and be careful not to fall.

725
00:47:52,904 --> 00:47:56,794
All right, thank you. I'll be sure to take it.

726
00:47:56,794 --> 00:47:58,504
Okay.

727
00:48:01,004 --> 00:48:06,404
