00:48:12,094 --> 00:48:14,164
W-What's wrong, Honey?

730
00:48:14,164 --> 00:48:15,594
Are you okay?

731
00:48:15,594 --> 00:48:19,934
Yes, I'm okay. It slipped out of my hand.

732
00:48:21,094 --> 00:48:25,364
