755
00:50:03,104 --> 00:50:04,624
- Dad! 
 - Honey, what's wrong?

756
00:50:04,624 --> 00:50:05,934
Dad! Dad!

757
00:50:05,934 --> 00:50:07,454
Honey.

758
00:50:09,424 --> 00:50:11,264
Dad...

759
00:50:12,974 --> 00:50:15,904
My poor dad.

760
00:50:16,684 --> 00:50:20,814
I feel so bad for my poor dad.

761
00:50:21,824 --> 00:50:23,684
Honey.

762
00:50:25,214 --> 00:50:27,194
Calm down.

763
00:50:27,194 --> 00:50:29,994
You had a dream about Father.

764
00:50:29,994 --> 00:50:32,744
Calm down. Calm down.

765
00:50:33,314 --> 00:50:38,814
That awful family. I never wanted to think about them again.

766
00:50:38,814 --> 00:50:46,244
